Din interface skulle behöva:
javascript// Node (Profile)
{
  id: "profile_techbro_ironic",
  label: "Tech Bro Ironic",
  
  // Visuellt
  size: antal_videos_i_profil,
  color: based_on_category,
  
  // Data
  videos: [...],
  mechanisms: {...},
  metadata: {
    description: "Din manual beskrivning",
    target_demo: "25-35, tech, urban",
    tone: "self-aware, cynical, high-energy"
  }
}

// Edge (Similarity)
{
  from: "profile_A",
  to: "profile_B",
  
  // Visuellt
  width: similarity_strength × 10,
  opacity: similarity_strength,
  
  // Data
  similarity: 0.75,
  reasoning: "Båda uppskattar timing-humor + tech-referenser",
  manual_override: true // Du satte detta manuellt
}
Interaktioner du behöver:

